main event: A civilian reported observing a small darkish object performing zigzagging maneuvers in Central Park, New York on June 15, 1966.
interesting points: The object moved so fast it appeared to be in multiple places at once., The observer described the object as being about the size of a basketball., The sighting lasted for approximately 90 seconds., The object seemed to come from a haze or vapor trail., The incident occurred on a clear day around 3:00 PM.
sighted object: a small darkish object performing zigzagging maneuvers
witness description: a civilian observing from a parked automobile
